Add Line Comment :                         Ctrl + / or ⌘
Search Everywhere:                         Double Shift
Reformat the Code:                         Ctrl+Alt+L or ⌥⌘L
Rename: Shift + F6
Generate code:                             Alt + Ins or ⌘+N or ⌃+Enter
